TYLER
v.
NC DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY 277P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 16, 2017 Casey Rafeal Tyler, for Tyler, Casey Rafeal. Amy Kunstling Irene, Special Deputy Attorney General, Kristy M. Newton, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 16th of August 2017 by Petitioner for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th of August 2017."
